@startuml
title Register Account Activity Diagram

start
:1. Open registration page;
:2. Enter user details;
:3. Validate input data;

if (4. Details valid?) then (Yes)
  :5. Create student account;
  :6. Store data in database;
  :7. Display success message;
else (No)
  :8. Show validation error;
endif

stop

note right
Activity Description:
1. User opens registration page.
2. User enters account details.
3. System validates the information.
4. System checks validity.
5. Account is created.
6. Data is saved in database.
7. Success message is displayed.
8. Error shown if validation fails.
end note
@enduml